race.comment: SATISFIED MUGS (1) has hit a purple patch this campaign putting dominant back-to-back wins together. Has three wins and a placing from five attempts over this course and distance and gets some well-needed weight relief with the 3kg claim. Rates the testing material against this line-up. BANG STICK (2) has placed two from three around this circuit and will strip fitter second-up from the break. Rates among the leading hopes. DRAGON TALES (3) loves this sprint journey with a win and three seconds from just four outings. Top-three commodity. OLD GOLD (5) has been racing well at Rockhampton at the past couple and can trouble the judge with any luck in running. EVAREADYMISS (9) saluted on debut and looks to have plenty of upside. In the mix.
